data.description: Enjoy main level living w/ an exceptional open floor plan concept, gourmet kitchen w/ stainless steel appliances, quartz counters, white cabinets, butler & walk-in pantry.  Wood flooring throughout main level, 9ft. ceilings, fireplace & built-ins in living room.  Eat-in kitchen with covered deck off kitchen and master bdrm.  Beautiful master retreat w/ large 5-pc bath & huge walk-in closet.  Garden level basement perfect for entertaining, with enormous rec rm, 2 add'l. bedrooms w/ bathroom and extra storage rooms. Close proximity to paths, trails, parks, recreation center, shops, restaurants and so much more.  The Farm offers a stunning setting with fantastic views of Pikes Peak and the front range throughout the neighborhood.  Coveted District 20 schools.
